-- Czech Telecoms Office Contacts Potential 4G Bidders, Euro Says
-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 2012-04-24T07:57:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-24/czech-telecoms-office-contacts-potential-4g-bidders-euro-says.html
The Czech Republic’s
telecommunication regulator approached potential Czech and
international bidders  with the conditions of a sale of 4G
frequencies in the country,  Euro  reported, citing agency’s head
Pavel Dvorak.  The regulator wrote to telecommunications companies such as
 China Mobile Ltd. (941)  or financial investors including Czech private
equity groups PPF AS, KKCG, J&T Finance Group, the weekly
newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague at 
 lponikelska1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  